annotations.caption: a group of men stand in the snow with skis . there are many snow covered trees behind the skiers . there is another group of men off in the distance . the skiers are all dressed in warm clothing . the sky above them is gray .

a small short haired brown dog walks down the street , holding a skateboard in its mouth . the boards underside is pink and aqua . its wheels are red . the dog has a body collar on it . its body has black spots .
theres a bottle of wine on the table with a black label . on the label or two hands open . there is a cracker and a coffee on a saucer . the table is made of light wood .

the image is of place setting on a table . the table is covered with a plastic cloth that has red , orange , and yellow stripes separated by white lines . there is a white plate that has orange noodles with broccoli on top of them . there is silverware on each side of the plate and the base to a glass is visible above the plate to the right .
there are two elephants standing on the ground . there are two people standing next to them . one of the elephants on the left has its leg raised up . there are green trees behind a fence .
there are several zebras drinking from a pond of water . there are small waves in the water . there are many rocks and dirt behind them on the ground .
there are two jets in the sky . one of them is leaving a red stream . another is leaving a blue stream . the sky is full of clouds .
a light brown teddy bear is sitting in a black chair . there is a white keyboard on the desk in front of them . there is a computer monitor on the desk above the keyboard that is turned on .
a very detailed hotel room . the bedding is blue and red and has floral designs . there is television in the corner and flowers sitting on the dresser .
three animals walking in a deep snow . there are markings in the snow up to where the animals are . there are mountains in the distancewith snow on them . the sky is blue with some cloud coverage .

beautiful elephants are showed at a festival of some sort , in asia . there is a row of the lovely animals , each draped in colorful blankets and headdress . young men , trainers , probably , stand in front , clad in orange outfits . families approach an elephant to admire . the elephants are shaded by rush awnings .

a man in a blue button down shirt is sitting in a chair on a cobblestone sidewalk outdoors . the man is holding and looking down at an electronic tablet . there are three other people sitting next to the man in a symmetrical line . two of the other people sitting next to the man in the blue shirt are holding silver and black laptops in their laps . one of the other people is also holding a electronic tablet . the bottom of a grey womans skirt , her legs and feet in grey shoes are visible behind a metal pole with four metal feet .

two young boys are playing ultimate frisbee in a green grassy field . the field is surrounded by green trees . one boy is wearing a red shirt and shorts and the other is wearing shorts and a tshirt . the red frisbee is being thrown in the air into a metal cage .
there are chefs making food . they are all wearing hats . the hats are all tall and white . there is a teacher teaching them things .
two people are palying tennis . they are both men . they have similar hair cuts . they are trying to hit a ball . their outfits are white in color .
there is a very tall building . there is a clock on the building . the clock is white . there are roman numerals on the clock . there is a metal gate around the clock .

a man and a child are lying together on a bed . the child is dressed in white and is sleeping on her back . the man is lying face down on the far side of the bed . he is wearing black patterned pants and white socks . the sheet on the bed is white , and there is a white sheet partially covering the two people . the headboard of the bed is a dark brown wood with carvings .

a large red cross country bus with luxury travel written on the windows is parked in front of a tan building . the driver side window on the bus is open . behind the bus there is a green and a blue mail box next to a large tree . in front of the bus there is a parking meter on a gray pole . there are no other cars visible on the street .

two cats sit riding in a car on a car ride adventure . one cat is light grey with stripes and light green eyes and white whiskers . the other darker grey cat is looking out the passenger window at the mountains outside . the cat has a red collar .

a tall large elephant is walking on a dirt road the elephant has long white tusk and a trunk that drag the ground . the elephant is crossing the road to get to the other side . the side of the road has a lot of bushes and trees .

the cental focal point of this kitchen is a black glass fronted stove . the stove has six burners as well as a silver top of a pan on the top of it . the floor is black and white tiled and the reflections of the tiles can be seen in the door of the stove . surrounding the stove are two white cabinets . the counter top on either side of the stove is wooden . and the knobs on the front of the stove are made of black plastic .
a man is outside in a tented area . the tents have light fixtures on their poles . there are a bunch of chairs and tables located underneath the tents as well . it is dark outside .

two teddy bears are sitting on a bed holding a big camera and a small camera . both cameras are black in color and branded nikon . the bed is made with butterfly s on the blanket and pillows to the side of the bed which are stacked on one another .
the image is of a person walking across a beam . they are wearing a tan shirt and pants with black gloves and hat on . the beam is located outside . snow is on the ground .

there is a black grill filled with hot charcoal . there is a wire rack above the fire and coals . there are eight sausages laying on the rack . the sausages range from a light brown color to dark brown .
some food is on top of a piece of silver tin foil . the foil has small bumps and is crumpled up towards the end . the food has cheese and broccoli on top of it .
a black and white pole has a red and white sign on it . there is a small fence behind the sign . there are trees behind the fence .

a tall stone tower is in front of a light blue sky . a white and blue flag flies above the tower . the stones are tan colored and have two moon decorations with a star in the middle . a circle white clock with black hands and numbers is on the front of the tower . there are also open arched windows on each side of the tower .

the bench is red with a black armrest . the armrest has a shape of a bird on it . on the bench are plants in the pots . beside the bench is a big plant . behind the plant is a wired fence . under the bench are bunch of dry leaves .
there is a white plate on top of the table . there is a glass on the table . there is salad on the plate . there is onions and carrots on top of the salad .
a man is flying an airplane . the airplane is blue and pretty old . there is a man standing on the very top of the plane with one leg and one arm up in the air .
there are two cats under the car . one cat is black behind him is a black and white cat . both cats are resting .
a black toilet is on the floor . the seat of the toilet is black and the tank is white . there is a roll of toilet paper on the back of the toilet .
two zebras wander a large , nearly grassless prairie . far beyond the prairie can be seen a row of trees . the sky over head is clear and blue .

two women are standing on the roof of a building flying a kite . the kite is shaped like a large bird and in tan in color . the wings of the kite have yellow and red accents . the woman directly under the kite is wearing a black coat with the hood drawn about her head . the second woman is standing away from the kite with one arm in the air . a grey plastic chair is next to the woman in the black jacket . a man is visible on a neighboring rooftop with his back to the women .

this photo is taken in a room . cords can be seen on the carpet . the leg and foot of a person can also be seen . the person is wearing a gray and yellow tennis shoe . there are two slices of pizza sitting on a white plate . one of the slices has been partially eaten . and under the white plate sits a white napkin .

a kitchen has some cabinets in it . the counter below them is empty . there is a white fridge in the corner . a sink sits in the middle of the counter . there is a living room next to the kitchen . there is a window in the living room . a tree is visible outside the window . there are many lights on in the kitchen . there is dishwasher in the kitchen .

there are four girls playing soccer on a soccer field . two of the girls are wearing orange shirts and orange socks and two of the girls are wearing striped black and red shirts and black socks . the girl in the orange shirt is kicking the white soccer ball .

a white plate sits on a table . the plate is filled with some food . there is some broccoli sitting on a slice of meat there is some sauce on the broccoli . the food is mixed together . the table looks to be dark .

a grand building is shown here . there is a tall tower with a clock . there is a communist hammer and sickle symbol on the front . to me , that suggests this building is located in china . shrubs are in front , and the sky overhead is cloudy . the structure dwarfs nearby buildings and streetlamps , which provide some sense of scale .

a boy wearing a green shirt and jean shorts . the boy has blonde hair and hes holding a green skate board . the skate board has yellow wheels on them . the street is behind the boy and is black . the boy is wearing brown shoes on his feet .
there are two clocks hanging on the wall . there is a small tree in between them on a table . the wall behind them is white .

a fluffy gray cat sits indoors on a bed , with sunlight coming in from a window off to the side . the cat has green eyes , and long whiskers . the cats tail is in the foreground , and the cats pupils look like black slits . the bedding is white , and there is some brown on the pillows in the background . there is a shadow on half of the cats face from the sunlight .

a bicycle is parked on the grass near water . there are bushes in front of the water that are bright green . there is a bridge going from one side of the river to the other and its made of stone . there are green trees on the other side of the river . the sky is blue .
there are two giraffes , three zebras and two ostriches in a pen . there is a wooden fence around the pen . there is a large building in front of the animals . there are tall trees behind the fence .

three people are in the kitchen . a man in a gray shirt is standing and his hands are in front of him , motioning as hes talking . next to him is a man in an orange hat , blue shirt and black jacket and he is sitting down . a woman with long hair is standing in the doorway to the kitchen . the counter is filled with food products .
a large red stop sign is above two guys . there is a brick building behind them . there is a street in front of the building that has cars lined on the street .

there is a baseball player preparing to throw the baseball . the player is wearing a white uniform with the word mets and the number 34 on the front . the players shoes are black and have a nike symbol on the side . the wall is blue with yellow advertisements on the wall . behind the wall is many seated spectators watching the game .
a panoramic view of a living room and dining area . the furniture in the living room is an off white color . the furniture in the dining area is a dark mahogany color .
a hand is on the mouse . the mouse is black in color . the thumb is on the side . there is a shadow under the hand .

the face of the clock is white with black numbers . the numbers are roman numeral numbers . theres a silver horse with a gold mean to the left of the clock and a gold lion wearing a crown to the right .

a triangle shaped tub is in the corner of a bathroom . it doubles as a shower . the shower head is hanging on the wall and it can removed and hand held . the on switch is circular and silver . there is a small white towel draped over the lip of the tub . the floor and walls are made of large grey tiles .
there are two african elephants in a clearing in the day time . only their heads and shoulders are visible . they are facing each other and their trunks are entwined .
there are people standing on a beach . there are houses in the distance on the sand . there is a black bird flying above the beach .
a small street food vendor has set up shop . it has a open sign that is on , to let people know they are open for business . on the sign it states they serve heros and mac & cheese .
a man is hitting a baseball . his uniform is blue . he is holding a white bat . there is a catcher behind him . the catchers mitt is black .
a woman is wearing skis . she is holding black ski poles in her hands . she is wearing a red jacket and a striped cap on her head . there are tracks in the snow behind her .
there is a large bed in a room with a tan comforter on it . there is a large window with two lamps on both sides of it . there are red chairs in the room in front of the window .

a male skateboarder is doing a trick on a skate ramp . he is wearing a helmet and safety gear on his elbows and knees . the skateboarder has his knees bent and his right hand is holding the back of the skateboard in order to do the trick . there are people playing basketball in the back of the ramp . cars are on the street next to the park . a chain link fence separated the park from the road . the skateboard ramp is made of wood and is very high to the ground .
there are two people surfing in the water . a person is standing on a white surfboard . the person is wearing a black wet suit . there is a large wave in the water .

four giraffe are seen in an enclosure of dirt in across the river from a large , busy city . one giraffe appears to be licking a large stone wall , and the other three are huddles together in the middle of the enclosure . off to the left a solitary zebra is sniffing along on the ground . a wooden fence closed the enclosure , and on the other side ware bushes and trees .

a white passenger train is sitting still on its tracks . another set of tracks sits to the trains right . graffiti has been painted on the train in the colors of green , purple , blue and red . the doors of the train are red . above the graffiti is the letter b in an oval and a number 2 .

a boy is doing a snow boarding on a big , blue tube . the boy is wearing a blue helmet . he is also wearing a yellow stripes , long sleeve shirt and a green pants . in a very far distance , the view of lights are visible .
a streetlight is displayed on green . there is a green street sign that reads lutz attached . the pole of the streetlight is a very clean silver metal color .
there is a large red truck on a street . there is a brown dog on the back of the truck . there is a silver box inside the truck . there are trees on the side of the truck .
a woman is wearing a purple long sleeved shirt with a red dress on . she is holding a blue bag and has a cell phone up to her ear . there is a wood building behind the person .
a woman is riding a horse . the horse is dark brown . she has on a black hoodie and helmet . the lady also has on black boots and gray leggings .

a black and white cow is standing in a field . the cow has a white face and has colorful tags in its ears . there is a hill with grass on it behind the cow .
two polar bears are standing next to each other . there is a large rock behind them . there is grass and dirt in front of them .

two people walking up a snowy mountain . one man is carrying a red ski and is wearing a gray jacket with red gloves . the man in the back is walking up the mountain wearing a gray jacket with dark scarf . the mountain has tracks of skis that have been there .
the train is pulling into the station . there is no one on the platform by the train . the front of the train is blue and gray . the conductor is driving the train .

a small table is shown behind glass with old fashioned barbers tools on it . there is a foam brush , a brush to remove the hairs , shears , a brush , a mirror and a nose hair trimmer . one of the brushes is in a white cup with a design on and some letters on it .

a small black and white boat traveling across a body of water . the bot has many port holes on it . there are large radio towers and communication equipment on the boat . there is a large green hillside directly behind the boat and the sky above is gray .

an orange kitten , with white fur on its chest , is laying on a pillow . the pillow is blue with a white and teal fish skeleton and several cats printed on it . the pillow the kitten is laying on is resting on top of a thin , blue knitted blanket . sunlight is shining on the blanket . the front paw of the kitten is crossed over the other , and it is looking at something with wide open eyes .
a sign is yellow in color . the sign has pictures on it . the hydrant is red in color . the sky is grey in color . there arent any leaves on the tree .

an outdoor fruit merchant is holding bunches of plantains or bananas . there many more bunches sitting on a mobile cart . the fruits are in various stages of ripeness . some are green while others are yellow with spots . the merchant is wearing a pink hat and a whitish t shirt . he appears to be smiling . an onlooker is sitting off in the distance .
a woman in an orange shirt is swinging a black bat . there is a man in a white shirt throwing a ball at her . there is a large house on the beach behind them .

an elephant walking in a meadow . the elephant has its back to us and it is walking towards a grouping of trees and low green bushes . the grass it walks through is tall and light green and there is a piece of wood stump sticking up near the edge of the field .
the sun has recently set in this area . a couple of boats are on the water . lights reflect on the water . a cruise ship is docked . a neon sign is above the cruise ship .

a surfboard is upside down on an old tree stump . the surfboard is being used as a planter , and different kids of plants are growing in dark soil on the bottom . the yard around it is overgrown with weeds , and various wild plants . in the rear there is an apartment building with different sizes of gates on the doors and and balconies .
there are many trains on the tracks . there are a lot of gray buildings on the other side of the trains . there is a hill with trees on it in front of the buildings .

a bench is sitting next to a plant . the plant is a small tree that is inside of a white square pot . behind them both is a brick building and some stone .
the window is white . behind the window are two cats looking outside . one cat is orange and the other one is gray . there are white curtains and the window frame is white .
there is a large gray and red building . there is a large clock on the building . there are cars parked in front of the building .
a group of people are ordering some food . the people are all dressed well . the sign on the side is yellow . the sign has pictures on it .

this image is of a fruit stand . no seller is present in the image . there are bananas in differing stages of ripeness and grapes hanging from plastic strings attached to wires . in baskets balanced on red plastic crates , there are oranges , apples and more bananas . there are also carrots , cucumbers , bananas and oranges arranged on trays . some lettuce and sweet potatoes are also for sale . in the left of the image , there is a metal basket that is probably used to weigh produce .
two planes are taking off . one plane is very red . there is a patch of grass next to the planes . the roads are grey . the sun is not shining .

a man is snowboarding down a hill . their are several evergreen trees in the background . his skis are green and black , while his jacket is red . their are mountains in the background . another skier in the background can be seen .
a black plate sits on a table . there is a slice of cake on the plate . there is a white plastic knife on top of the plate . there is colorful frosting on top of the cake .

there is a white boat in the sand next to some water . there are waves in the water behind the boat . there are tracks in the sand in front of a boat .
a man wearing a white lab coat is looking down at a laptop that is on a counter . the man has dark hair . the laptop is silver . there is another person behind him looking at a laptop .

a room has various furniture items stored in it . there is a red leather couch with a pillow on top of it , a chester drawer , wooden chairs and a box from a tv . the walls of the room are dirty and old . there is a door through which one can see other rooms and another doorway . to the right of the doorway is a white radiator .
there are several cars parked in a parking lot . there are two birds on the ground in front of the cars . there are trees behind the parking lot .

a woman is wearing a black jacket and a blue cap . she is sitting on a wooden table . there is a blue plastic water bottle on the table next to her . she is holding a sandwich . there are ski poles leaning up against the table .

the image is in black and white . it is looking down a long road that is smoother on the left side but has pot holes full of water and gravel on the right side . up close there are two men . they are each riding mopeds that have sticks tide to the back . the sticks are from side to side and there are dead chickens hanging down from them . the chickens are attached to the sticks by their feet . the nearest man doesnt have a shirt on and he is the one hauling the chickens . the man on the other scooter has a lightweight long sleeve shirt on and his sticks are empty . they are riding away down the road . in the distance the sky is very cloudy . along the left side there are buildings and some palm trees . there is also a man riding in the opposite direction on a bicycle . he is wearing a long sleeve shirt and pants . there are power lines running along the road and across it in a few places . further off in the distance there is also another person riding a scooter in the same direction as the two men that are up close .

a man wearing a suit and black glasses is standing outside . behind the man is a building . the building has a antique look to it . the man has on a plum colored tie . the man is wearing a white shirt and a dark colored blazer . the short brown haired man has a raised lip expression as if he is not happy . the day is sunny .

a wooden , gray pole is standing beside a red fire hydrant . the hydrant is red with blue cap . across the street is a couple walking at the sidewalk . the woman is wearing a white shirt and carrying black shoulder bag .
this a portrait of a man . the background is green . the hair of the man is brown . he is wearing a brown collard shirt .
a shower with a glass door in a bathroom . the shower head is silver . there is a shelf in front of the door with a rolled up white towel . there is a white phone on the wall .

there are two striped zebras standing on the dirt . there is a log behind them on the ground . there is a tree trunk on the ground behind them .

a girl is looking at the camera . she is located near a black bench . she has a blue bag in her hand and is wearing a black coat . she has a small pink bow in her head .

there is a yellow train on the tracks . there is also a shadow on the platform . there is open space above the roof . there is a window on the back of the train . there is a small yellow door as well .

a dark brown horse stands tall . the horse is well groomed , wearing a saddle and bridle . its garments are black leather and silver metal . behind the horse is dirt , and behind the dirt is a slight mound of sand and grass . far in the distance seems to be a line of dark forest . the sky above is blue with large fluffy white clouds .

a bus is blue and white , with the blue painted like waves . the front of the bus has an orange digitized sign with the destination name and number of bus . the bus is traveling on a gray paved road . tall green trees are on the side of the road .
a yellow truck is sitting in the road , it looks like it is stopped at a traffic light . there is a bus beside it and next to a big building which is red and white .

a man and a kid is on the snow . the man is kneeling on his knees watching the little kid . the kid is wearing a goggles on his head and looking at the man . the kid is also wearing ski boards that is covered with snow . behind the snow covered field is a fence . further down are people and red umbrellas . much further , behind the people are two buildings .
two horses are behind a fence . one horse is brown . that horse is also wearing a mask . the other horse is white and spotted . his feet are dark brown .
the container of food is broccoli and cheese . there is a silver food in the container . the broccoli is green and is covered with yellow cheese .
a white plate is sitting on a wooden table . on the plate is two sandwiches . next to the sandwiches are a tomato and a piece of lettuce .
a white fridge is in a room next to a yellow counter top . there is a roll of paper towels above the counter .

two ducks and three ducklings is seen in a lake on a bright day . in front of the ducks there is a wooden pier extending into the water . on the right in front of the camera is a brown pole with a white point on the top , and a black letter e on a white background attached to the pole .

an airplane is flying in the blue sky . the plane is white with yellow engines on the wings . the tail of the plane has black dots . the logo on the plane says vueling . the wing tips on the airplane are also yellow , matching the engines .

a man is in a blue and white checkered shirt and eye glasses is pouring sauce on a plate at a dining table in a restaurant . the man is sitting across from another man . the other man is wearing a black shirt and looking down at a menu . both men are sitting at a long wooden table . the man in the checkered shirt is sitting on a green seat attached to the wall . the man in the black shirt is sitting in a single black chair . the restaurant has windows for walls and green foliage is visible form the table the men are seated at . above the man in the checkered shirt is a yellow light attached to the wall .
several people are skiing down a hill . one of the men has yellow sunglasses on . there are tall skinny trees behind them .
a giraffe is encaged in a zoo area . the giraffe is a little bit dirty in appearance . the giraffe is eating from a little feeding area that is attached on the wall .
a hot dog is sitting on a foil wrapper . the wrapper is on top of a metal counter . there is a container that says onions on it hanging above the hot dog .

a grey truck is parked on the gravel shoulder of a paved tree covered mountain pass . two metal , ladderlike ramps are leaning onto the bed of the truck as a way to drive 4wheel atv vehicles onto the vehicle . a red and yellow atv is parked on top of the truck bed . a dark colored atv is parked on the ground behind the truck . to the left of the truck is a stop sign . adjacent to the stop sign is a dirt bike .

a fighter jet sits still on a runway . there are two lights that are near the landing gear that is lit up . there are trees far in the distance and a lot of grass that is short in the foreground . the jet is grey with blue markings and or symbols on the side . there appears to be one pilot in the cockpit .

there is a tall brown grandfather clock up against a white wall . the clock has a gold face but the numbers are silver and black hands . there is glass exposing the gold pulleys that work the clock . to the right of the clock is a blue fabric chair with wooden legs . the floor is a brown carpet . there is the left trim of a window visible , but only a very small corner of the window is visible .
a blue plate with slices of oranges on it . there is a red bowl on top of the plate . there are blueberries inside of the bowl .

four women all dressed the same occupy a small living space . the women are dressed in dark jumpsuits and blue checked shirts . a white couch and chair sit on a wooden floor with a wooden coffee table in front of them . white curtains cover the windows .
there is a white plate on a blue table . there is a slice of pizza on the plate with a pepperoni on it . there is a red sauce on the plate next to the pizza .
there is a small pink and white tea pot siting next to a small tea cup and plate . there is cookies and a large cupcake in front of the tea pot . they are sitting on top of a white cake .
there are seven people lined up for a photo . there is six females and one male . the male is wearing a gray suit .

a black fluffy dog is running across wet , dark beige sand . the dogs fur is wet and dripping with water . the dog is holding a red , white and blue ball in its mouth . the dogs tail is upright in the air and he is casting a black shadow on the sand beneath him . a black shadow is on the ground behind his shadow . the additional shadow is in the shape of a human being . a small reflection of water and ripples is at the base of the sand behind the dog .
there is a blue and white trolley on the tracks . there are wires hanging above the trolley . there are two large brick buildings behind the trolley .

an injured elephant is laying in a brown body of water . there are spots of blood on his head and trunk the size of a mans hand , and one on his front visible leg . the leg with the blood is in chains . a man in pants and a dress button down shirt stands at the head of the elephant wiping his head with a cloth . close the camera a boy in an orange shirt and blue pants looks away from the elephant .

a black umbrella sits near a grey stone wall . the umbrellas is suspended one foot in the air . a wooden bench is attached to the grey stone wall . above the bench is a yellow and white sign with black writing and a green and orange map . the ceiling above the bench is made of glass and metal and reveals daylight . the ground beneath the bench is made of paved cobblestone walkway . a blue laminated sign hangs from the ceiling near the umbrella . the umbrella has a checkered pattern . the umbrella is hooked around a metal pole with a square base .
a black motorcycle with a red stripe down it is parked . there are cars in front of the motorcycle . one of the cars is blue and the other one is red .

a glass bowl holds some exotic fruits . there is a bunch of ripening bananas , and a papaya . also , there is one common in thailand , a dragon fruit with beautiful hot pink peel . a pineapple top can be seen in the background .

four zebras are in a mowed grass field . two zebras are walking towards the camera . one is an adult , and other one is smaller . the other tow zebras are walking behind the first two , but traveling towards the left of the frame . the back half of another animal is also visible in the top left corner .

the cat is looking at the camera . its nose is light pink . the eyes are yellow with black pupil . the top head of the cat is is black and brown while the lower part is white . the cats whiskers are white .

inside the subway is a still picture of a white subway train trimmed in black . on the train is the number 246 . in front and to the side of the train is a woman with a headdress . she is wearing a long skirt and a plaid jacket . there is an asian man in the picture . he is carrying a messenger bag . he is wearing a light colored shirt , white shorts , and white shoes . he is carrying a water bottle . there are florescent lights on in the subway . on the bottom is miezzcom photography .
a white paper plate with a colorful frosted donut on top of it . there is a white napkin behind the plate and they are sitting on top of the wood table .
a small white airplane is in the sky . there are stripes on the side of the airplane . there is writing on the tail of the airplane . there are small windows on the plane .
people are standing in front of a tree . there is a man with a black hat on . there is a woman with a red shirt on . there are two kids standing next to them .

this is a crowded ocean beach with many people walking around . there is a woman up close in a lifeguard stand watching over the beach , with other lifeguard stands lining the beach in the distance . seagulls are standing on the beach as well as flying above the people . high rise buildings are in the background .
there is a large red bus on the street . there is a white building next to the bus . there are people walking on the street behind the bus . the bus has a yellow mirror on it .

a cake is getting ready to be cut into . the cake has a man with a pirate hat on and eye patch smiling with a green shirt . on the very top of the cake is a bigger face with the same person making a weird gestured face .
a man is cooking at a counter . he is wearing a red shirt . the shorts he is wearing are blue . he has high white socks .
